  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00001",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人引陈元礼同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "陈元礼"
      ],
      "text": "金戈铁马扬飞乌，猛将齐驱下国都。管教乱贼归吾掌，方显人间大丈夫。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈元礼"
      ],
      "text": "俺，右龙武将陈元礼是也。只因安禄山造反，圣驾西巡，命俺统禁军，护驾西行，前面已是栈道了。嘚，众将官！",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "有！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈元礼"
      ],
      "text": "好生护驾者！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下，高力士上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "请万岁爷缓辔而行。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "唐明皇上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "武陵花",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "万里巡行，多少凄凉途路情！看云山重迭处，似我乱愁交并。无边落木响秋声，长空孤雁添悲哽！",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "寡人自离马嵬坡，饱尝辛苦。前日遣使臣赍奉玺册，传位太子去了。行了月余，将近蜀中，且喜贼兵渐远，可以缓程而进。只是对此乌啼花落，水绿山青，无非助朕悲怀，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "万岁爷途路风霜，十分劳顿，请自排遣，幸勿过伤。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "高力士。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "朕与妃子，坐则并几，行则随肩，今日仓卒西巡，断送她这般结果，教寡人如何撇得下也！",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "武陵花",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "提起伤心事，泪如倾。回望马嵬坡下，不觉恨填膺，袅袅旗旌，背残日期风摇影。匹马崎岖怎么暂停？怎么暂停？只见黄埃散漫天昏暝。哀猿断肠，听子规叫血，好教人怕听。兀的不惨煞人也么哥！兀的不惨煞人也么哥！萧条怎生？",
      "text_length": 102
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "雨来了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "武陵花",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "峨嵋山下少人经，冷雨斜风扑面迎。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈元礼上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈元礼"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，暂往剑阁避雨者！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同呐喊，同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "独自登临意转伤，蜀山蜀水恨茫茫。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "应风雨声。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "不知何处风吹雨，点点声声迸断肠！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "应铃声。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "听那壁厢不住的声响，聒得人好不耐烦！高力士。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "看何物声响？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "应铃声。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902131",
      "scene_id": "70902131_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁爷：是树林中雨声，和那檐前铃铎，随风而响。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902131_e00032",
